  "body": "### Description\n_Type_: Bug\n\n_Summary_: after crash in offline mode when generating mnemoinc phrase during sign up, I can't find a way to continue - tried with `keycard-cli` and with application - in both cases can't connect to card.\n\n#### Expected behavior\nCan continue after go back online\n\n#### Actual behavior\nApplication is crashed. \n\nAfter this crash I'm unable to use this card anymore.\nIf I try to use `keycard-cli delete -l debug` or `./keycard-cli install -l debug cap.cap` tool is hanging on step:\n\n```\n./keycard-cli delete -l debug\nINFO [04-03|17:37:46.083] waiting for a card package=status-go/cmd/keycard\nINFO [04-03|17:37:46.085] card found package=status-go/cmd/keycard index=0\nDEBUG[04-03|17:37:46.085] using reader package=status-go/cmd/keycard name=\"ACS ACR 38U-CCID\"\nDEBUG[04-03|17:37:46.085] connecting to card package=status-go/cmd/keycard reader=\"ACS ACR 38U-CCID\"\n```\n\nIf I try to create account using .apk, application is hanging on \"Preparing card\" stage.\n\n### Reproduction\n\n\n* Open Status\n* Tap on create account -> Keycard\n* Create PIN\n* On stage \"Preparing card\" go to Airplane mode\n* on \"PUK and Pair Codes\" tap next\n* On stage of \"Generating mnemonic phrase\" tap try again \n\n### Additional Information\n\n\n* Status version: 0.12.0 apk http://status-im-prs.ams3.digitaloceanspaces.com/StatusIm-190402-123212-80ef5d-pr.apk\n* Operating System: Android 8, LG V20\n* Keycard-cli: https://github.com/status-im/keycard-cli/releases/tag/0.0.1, cap: https://github.com/status-im/status-keycard/releases/tag/2.1.1 (installed with https://gist.github.com/gravityblast/8c7472dcf86f7b23c797b79c2dbc1d0a)\n\n#### Logs\nUnfortunately, I can't fetch logs for this device - adb is not working.\n\n",
